trans-unit.source: Specifies the context keyword for a class or member.
trans-unit.target: 指定一个类或成员的上下文关键字。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 此类不能被继承。

trans-unit.source: By default, the Help keyword for a class is given by the <xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property value.
trans-unit.target: 默认情况下，给定类的帮助关键字<xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>属性值。</xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For members, the Help keyword is given by the full name of the type that declared the property, plus the property name itself.
trans-unit.target: 对于成员，声明属性的类型的完整名称加上属性名称本身由给定的 Help 关键字。

trans-unit.source: For example, consider the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> control.
trans-unit.target: 例如，考虑<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName>控件。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The class keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button", but the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text", because the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=fullName> class, rather than the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> class itself; the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> class inherits the property.
trans-unit.target: 类关键字是"System.Windows.Forms.Button"，但<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>属性关键字是"System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text"，因为<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>上声明属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=fullName>类，而不是<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName>类本身;<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName>类继承属性。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: By contrast, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> class, so its keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult".
trans-unit.target: 与此相反，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=fullName>上声明属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName>类，因此其关键字是"System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult"。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When the Help system gets the keywords, it will first look at HelpKeywordAttribute.
trans-unit.target: 当帮助系统获取的关键字时，它将首先查看 HelpKeywordAttribute。

trans-unit.source: At the class level, it will return the string specified by the HelpKeywordAttribute.
trans-unit.target: 在类级别，它将返回指定 HelpKeywordAttribute 的字符串。

trans-unit.source: This will not be used for members of the type in question, which will still reflect the declaring type's actual full name, plus the member name.
trans-unit.target: 这将不用于所涉及的类型，它仍反映的声明类型的实际的完整名称，加上成员名称的成员。

trans-unit.source: This attribute supports strongly typed classes that have associated common documentation but distinct Help IDs.
trans-unit.target: 此属性支持具有相关联的常见文档但帮助 Id 的不同状态的强类型的类。
